Key Match Events: Quinton de Kock scored 74 runs, Kagiso Rabada took 3 wickets, Andries Gous scored an unbeaten 80
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the first Super Eight match for USA in the ICC Men's T20 World Cup 2024
Others: South Africa won the match by 18 runs, scoring 194/4 and restricting USA to 176/6
